OL,3,CLorry driver's actions save life of
OL,4,Chomeless man found asleep in
OL,5,Cindustrial bin
OL,7,FWatch: The moment a man is found
OL,8,Fsleeping in a bin was caught on CCTV.
OL,10,FThe quick thinking actions of a
OL,11,FBanbury lorry driver have been
OL,12,Fpraised, after he discovered a
OL,13,Fhomeless man asleep in an industrial
OL,14,Fbin he was about to empty.
OL,16,FDave Goodwin found the rough sleeper
OL,17,Finside the bin, when he realised it
OL,18,Fwas heavier than expected, and decided
OL,19,Fto investigate why.
