OL,7,FIt was then he noticed the man under
OL,8,Fpiles of rubbish, who had taken refuge
OL,9,Finside the bin, to shelter from cold
OL,10,FDecember temperatures.
OL,12,FGrundon Waste Management, who Dave
OL,13,Fworks for, say his decision to look
OL,14,Finside the bin prevented a tragic
OL,15,Faccident.
