OL,4,Chomeless man found asleep in
OL,5,Cindustrial bin
OL,7,FRecalling the experience, Dave, who is
OL,8,Fbased at a depot in Banbury, said: "As
OL,9,Fdrivers, we are always trained to be
OL,10,Falert to anything unusual and it was
OL,11,Fone of those split second moments when
OL,12,Fyou realise something isn't right.
OL,14,F"I immediately stepped back from the
OL,15,Fbin and was hugely relieved to find
OL,16,Fthat although the gentleman inside was
OL,17,Fa bit shaken up, he was unharmed.
