OL,3,CLorry driver's actions save life of
OL,4,Chomeless man found asleep in
OL,5,Cindustrial bin
OL,7,F"He told me that previously, he would
OL,8,Flisten out for the sound of a diesel
OL,9,Fengine as a warning of a vehicle
OL,10,Fapproaching. Because I was in an
OL,11,Felectric vehicle, which is much
OL,12,Fquieter, he didn't hear it approach."
OL,14,FThe company has now joined forces with
OL,15,FCrisis, and has launched a campaign
OL,16,Fcalled 'The risks of Sleeping in Bins'.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@eO]
