OL,4,Chomeless man found asleep in
OL,5,Cindustrial bin
OL,7,FIt will see the introduction of
OL,8,Fbrightly-coloured warning stickers
OL,9,Furging people not to sleep inside
OL,10,Fbins, as well as making people aware
OL,11,Fthat someone may have taken refuge
OL,12,Finside.
OL,14,FGrundon says typical signs that
OL,15,Fsomeone may be taking refuge inside a
OL,16,Fbin will include broken locks, rubbish
OL,17,Fscattered on the ground or evidence of
OL,18,Fpersonal belongings nearby.
