OL,7,FReg Hodson, Head of Safety, Health,
OL,8,FEnvironment & Quality, from Grundon
OL,9,Fsaid: "Thankfully, due to Dave's
OL,10,Fprofessionalism and care no harm was
OL,11,Fdone but hearing his story and seeing
OL,12,Fthis video made us realise that, as
OL,13,Four industry moves to quieter electric
OL,14,Fwaste collection vehicles, we all need
OL,15,Fto be more vigilant to help reduce the
OL,16,Fchances of such an incident happening
OL,17,Fagain.
