OL,7,FFrancesca Albanese, Director of Policy
OL,8,Fand Social Change at Crisis said: "We
OL,9,Fare tragically seeing more and more
OL,10,Fpeople forced to sleep on our streets.
OL,11,FFaced with danger and uncertainty,
OL,12,Fpeople can seek shelter from the cold
OL,13,Fand to keep themselves hidden from
OL,14,Fview for their own safety.
OL,16,F"We are pleased to be able to work
OL,17,Fwith Grundon on this campaign, which
OL,18,Fwe hope will keep more people safe
OL,19,Ffrom harm."
